<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome - Online Voting System</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 30px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background: #004aad;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 22px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 25px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content h2 {
        color: #004aad;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .highlight {
        background: #f0f4ff;
        padding: 12px;
        border-left: 4px solid #004aad;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .steps {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        background: #f3f3f3;
        padding: 15px;
        font-size: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Online Voting System</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>

        <p>Welcome to the <strong>Online Voting System</strong>. Your voter account has been successfully created.</p>

        <div class="highlight">
          <strong>Registered Email:</strong> {{email}}</p>
        </div>

        <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Log in using your registered email.</li>
          <li>Verify your profile details.</li>
          <li>Stay tuned for election announcements.</li>
        </ol>

        <p>If you did not sign up, please contact our support team immediately.</p>

        <p>Thank you for being a part of transparent and secure digital voting!</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br/>
        <strong>Online Voting System Team</strong></p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} Online Voting System. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>